text: Nemo is a 1984 film directed by Arnaud Sélignac. It is also known as Dream One. ==Cast== *Jason Connery *Mathilda May *Harvey Keitel. ==Production== Goldcrest Films invested £2,099,000 in the film and received £1,482,000, making a loss of £617,000. ==References== ==External links== *Nemo at Letterbox DVD * Category:1984 films
title: Nemo (1984 film)
